de.esoco.process.ui.graphics

Enum UiStandardIcon

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<UiStandardIcon>
      • de.esoco.process.ui.graphics.UiStandardIcon
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    UiIconSupplier, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<UiStandardIcon>

    public enum UiStandardIcon
extends java.lang.Enum<UiStandardIcon>
implements UiIconSupplier
    An enumeration of some standard icons that are used internally by the process UI API. Applications must register a mapping to a specific icon library by invoking registerIconMapping(Function) to make the standard icons available.
